                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li xml:id="auto_2d2u60ho">
                        <p xml:id="auto_wvirlb4l">
                            <m>sin\,45.5^\circ</m>
                        </p>
                        <p xml:id="auto_spmagud9">
                            Locate <m>45.5^\circ</m>in the sine and cosine table.
                        </p>
                        <p xml:id="auto_8boimk2k">
                            Read the corresponding sine value. That is <me>sin\,45.5^\circ= 0.7133</me>,
                        </p>
                        <p xml:id="auto_6x64rco9">
                            <m>cos\,45.5^\circ</m>
                        </p>
                        <p xml:id="auto_v0p3ehg5">
                            Read the corresponding cosine value. That is <me>cos\,45.5^\circ= 0.7009</me>,
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li xml:id="auto_jj665jz0">
                        <p xml:id="auto_ywwo2kg9">
                            
                            <m>sin\,75.67^\circ</m>
                        </p>
